General.Name: Associate Global Partners Limited
General.Description: Associate Global Partners Limited is a publicly owned investment manager. It manages large cap, mid cap, small cap, micro cap, and income focused mandates for its institutional clients. The company was formerly known as Contango Asset Management Limited and changed its name to Associate Global Partners Limited in November 2022. Associate Global Partners Limited is based in Sydney, Australia.
General.Address: Level 35, 60 Margaret Street, Sydney, NSW, Australia, 2000
